Package io.atlasmap.spi

Interface AtlasInternalSession.Head

Enclosing interface:
AtlasInternalSession
public static interface AtlasInternalSession.Head
The AtlasInternalSession.Head object represents what is under processing right now. AtlasContext processes each mapping contained in AtlasMapping one-by-one and this AtlasInternalSession.Head represents which one of Mapping is under processing, as well as source field and target field.
